@Thisiscoolright Instead, you criticize the work of hundreds of thousands of people, while neither understanding it nor researching it.
@Thisiscoolright I read the article. If you want to criticize bootcamps, make an article focused on that. That would hang together.
@TechCrunch @Thisiscoolright A clickbait headline to stir controversy, around totally noncontroversial ideas like computational thinking
